What's new in 2.02?

I have reduced the memory consumption. I tested with 504 k chip and 540 k
fast and it worked. So, it just MIGHT work with half meg chip Amiga 500's
if installed and run from floppy... but I don't have a chance to try it
right now. If anybody does... let me know!